Package de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.evaluableexpressions.util

Utility classes to work with Evaluable Expressions.

See: Description

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AbstractEvaluableExpressionVisitor
    Abstract EvaluableExpressionVisitor offering a convenient interface.
    EvaluableExpressionSimplifier
    Produces shorter versions of unnecessarily complex EvaluableExpressions.
    ModifyingEvaluableExpressionVisitor
    A visitor allowing to create a new EvaluableExpression out of an existing one.
    RecursiveEvaluableExpressionVisitor
    Visitor of EvaluableExpressions, recursively visiting all their inner expressions.

Package de.uka.ipd.sdq.beagle.core.evaluableexpressions.util Description

Utility classes to work with Evaluable Expressions. The package contains helpers to analyse, read and modify them.
